verse.lines:
Kindly heaven smiles above,
When there’s love at home;
All the world is filled with love,
When there’s love at home;
Sweeter sings the brooklet by,
Brighter beams the azure sky;
Oh, there’s One who smiles on high
When there’s love at home.
Refrain 6:
Love at home, love at home;
Oh, there’s One who smiles on high
When there’s love at home.
